name: AudioClip

properties.name: audioFormat
properties.description: The audio format of the clip (sample rate bit depth channel layout)

properties.name: duration
properties.description: The duration of the clip measured in samples at the multitrack document's sample rate.

properties.name: selected
properties.description: Selection state of this audio clip.

properties.name: sourceChannelRouting
properties.description: Mapping of source channels to clip channels. The array contains indices of source channels which are routed to the according clip channels. The array has to have as many source channel indices as there are clip channels. Each source channel can be routed to exactly one clip channel.

properties.name: startTime
properties.description: The start time of the clip measured in samples at the multitrack document's sample rate.

description: An object representing a particular audio clip as part of a multitrack session.
